383
00:36:47,340 --> 00:36:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] nisu bili zadovoljni,

384
00:36:49,119 --> 00:36:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili kad nisam naišla na reakciju

385
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] koju si možda htjela dobit,

386
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:57,860
[SPEAKER_00] i kako si to ti odigrala,

387
00:36:57,860 --> 00:36:58,900
[SPEAKER_00] završila.

388
00:36:58,900 --> 00:37:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je, jer sam, ja možda previše,

389
00:37:01,639 --> 00:37:03,019
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam letala u svem tome,

390
00:37:03,019 --> 00:37:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] te sve emocije, ja sam letala

391
00:37:05,440 --> 00:37:07,139
[SPEAKER_01] i možda sam previše poletjela,

392
00:37:07,139 --> 00:37:10,460
[SPEAKER_01] pa zato sam bila i povrijeđena,

393
00:37:10,460 --> 00:37:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] zato što nisam dobila pravu reakciju,

394
00:37:12,539 --> 00:37:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali kod sam ja da meni ljudi hvala

395
00:37:14,579 --> 00:37:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] i da mu se zahvaljuju zbog nečeg dobrog

396
00:37:16,380 --> 00:37:18,400
[SPEAKER_01] što sam učinila, da bi ja bila radosna,

397
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:20,579
[SPEAKER_01] ono, nisam to trebala ni očekivati.

398
00:37:20,579 --> 00:37:22,360
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, danas kad to gledam tako,

399
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:25,019
[SPEAKER_01] bila sam u dosta situacija povrijeđena,

400
00:37:25,019 --> 00:37:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] ok, to je ljudski,

401
00:37:26,159 --> 00:37:28,820
[SPEAKER_01] ali uopće ne krivim danas te ljude,

402
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] zato što ni oni nisu znali bolje,

403
00:37:30,699 --> 00:37:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, nisu možda ni osjetili potrebu,

404
00:37:33,539 --> 00:37:35,679
[SPEAKER_01] da trebaju reći hvala za neke stvari

405
00:37:35,679 --> 00:37:37,699
[SPEAKER_01] koje sam ja, ono, slomila se,

406
00:37:37,699 --> 00:37:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] da dođem, doprem nekako do svega toga,

407
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:42,800
[SPEAKER_01] ali, ono, pa,

408
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:44,639
[SPEAKER_01] u ostalom ja sam to radila,

409
00:37:44,639 --> 00:37:46,360
[SPEAKER_01] zato što sam se lijepo isičala

410
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:50,239
[SPEAKER_01] više zbog toga, nego možda i zbog tih ljudi samih,

411
00:37:50,239 --> 00:37:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] jer da nije bilo tih ljudi, možda bi pronašla neke druge

412
00:37:53,119 --> 00:37:54,980
[SPEAKER_01] kojima bi to uradila, tako da,

413
00:37:54,980 --> 00:37:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] danas nemam ništa, ono, da kažem,

414
00:37:58,019 --> 00:38:00,179
[SPEAKER_01] loše što je to dogodilo,

415
00:38:00,179 --> 00:38:01,719
[SPEAKER_01] sve sam nekako prihvatila.

416
00:38:01,719 --> 00:38:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] A ko ti je bio najveća podrška

417
00:38:03,980 --> 00:38:05,780
[SPEAKER_00] u tom cijelom procesu,

418
00:38:05,780 --> 00:38:07,300
[SPEAKER_00] dok se sve to odigravalo,

419
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:10,559
[SPEAKER_00] kako su tvoji najbliži na to reagirali,

420
00:38:10,559 --> 00:38:12,480
[SPEAKER_00] budući da, ono, i nemate doma,

421
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:15,239
[SPEAKER_00] i nekako sve se odigrava,

422
00:38:15,239 --> 00:38:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] i to je tvoj centar svijeta tada.

423
00:38:18,139 --> 00:38:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da, kako si rekla, ono,

424
00:38:20,519 --> 00:38:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] da ste zvali jednom u trivitru,

425
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:23,659
[SPEAKER_00] da je stigla neka akcija

426
00:38:23,659 --> 00:38:25,739
[SPEAKER_00] i da si morala ići.

427
00:38:25,739 --> 00:38:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] I, ono, samo ta percepcija

428
00:38:27,960 --> 00:38:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] djevojka od 19 godina

429
00:38:31,500 --> 00:38:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] koja, ono, ima faksima i sve, ono, nešto.

430
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] Je, znači, bilo je tih nekih,

431
00:38:37,579 --> 00:38:39,500
[SPEAKER_01] baš teških trenutaka, ono,

432
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:41,019
[SPEAKER_01] koje nija nisam razumila,

433
00:38:41,019 --> 00:38:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, neko pošalje iz njemačke donaciju

434
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:46,500
[SPEAKER_01] i zove me, ono, vozača u topsovu trivitru,

435
00:38:46,500 --> 00:38:48,139
[SPEAKER_01] kaže, ja sam tu i tu možete doći,

436
00:38:48,139 --> 00:38:49,420
[SPEAKER_01] vaše ime je napisano,

437
00:38:49,420 --> 00:38:50,659
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ću doći.

438
00:38:50,659 --> 00:38:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] I je bilo je stvarno, ono,

439
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] nekih i smješnih i neugodnih iskustava.

440
00:38:55,539 --> 00:38:57,400
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, ne znam, ono,

441
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:59,440
[SPEAKER_01] mami sam zahvalna zato što stvarno,

442
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:02,099
[SPEAKER_01] ono, ja dođem svakas posla,

443
00:39:02,099 --> 00:39:03,579
[SPEAKER_01] pojedem, idem, rad,

444
00:39:03,579 --> 00:39:05,320
[SPEAKER_01] nisam mala neke obaveze u kući.

445
00:39:07,579 --> 00:39:09,679
[SPEAKER_01] U ovom period, dok su bile najaktivnije,

446
00:39:09,679 --> 00:39:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] dok je bila najaktivnija zajednica,

447
00:39:12,500 --> 00:39:14,780
[SPEAKER_01] ono, nisam imala nekako

448
00:39:14,780 --> 00:39:16,320
[SPEAKER_01] previše obaveze u kući,

449
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,440
[SPEAKER_01] mama je to nosila.

450
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:19,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam stvarno trudila biti tada

451
00:39:19,780 --> 00:39:21,260
[SPEAKER_01] i djevojka i prijateljice,

452
00:39:21,260 --> 00:39:24,219
[SPEAKER_01] da moji prijatelji i koliko toliko obitelj,

453
00:39:24,219 --> 00:39:25,860
[SPEAKER_01] uopće, ono, to ne osjeti sve to.

454
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:27,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam, mislim,

455
00:39:27,260 --> 00:39:29,300
[SPEAKER_01] ti malo prije govoriš, onaj,

456
00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:31,400
[SPEAKER_01] odrekla se izlazaka

457
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:32,599
[SPEAKER_01] i druženja, nisam.

458
00:39:32,659 --> 00:39:34,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam, odradim sve to,

459
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:35,679
[SPEAKER_01] izađem s prijateljima,

460
00:39:35,679 --> 00:39:36,820
[SPEAKER_01] budem stonjem,

461
00:39:36,820 --> 00:39:38,159
[SPEAKER_01] vratim se kući,

462
00:39:38,159 --> 00:39:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] sve sam nekako, ono,

463
00:39:39,980 --> 00:39:41,559
[SPEAKER_01] nisam htjela da niko osjeti

464
00:39:41,559 --> 00:39:42,199
[SPEAKER_01] da me nema.

465
00:39:42,199 --> 00:39:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] Najviše se osjetili samo zato

466
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:46,360
[SPEAKER_01] što se, ono, moral nekad im je žao bilo,

467
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] pa eto, ono,

468
00:39:47,039 --> 00:39:50,519
[SPEAKER_01] iz ljubavi, a iz podrške meni,

469
00:39:50,519 --> 00:39:52,179
[SPEAKER_01] ono, svi su dolazili volantirati.

470
00:39:52,179 --> 00:39:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ja mislim da moj toni

471
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:55,380
[SPEAKER_01] nikad ne bi negdje volantirao,

472
00:39:55,380 --> 00:39:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] da mu nije bilo žao mene,

473
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:58,199
[SPEAKER_01] ono, koliko se lovim tu

474
00:39:58,199 --> 00:40:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] i stvarno uvijek je bio tu

475
00:40:00,019 --> 00:40:01,920
[SPEAKER_01] i odvezi i dovezi i ponesi

476
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:03,320
[SPEAKER_01] i sigurno, ono,

477
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,940
[SPEAKER_01] nije mu uvijek bilo zanimljivo

478
00:40:04,940 --> 00:40:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] doći u Muranskosla

479
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:09,199
[SPEAKER_01] i razvozati neke humanitarne,

480
00:40:09,199 --> 00:40:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] niti zna gdje, kome vozi,

481
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:11,300
[SPEAKER_01] niti šta,

482
00:40:11,300 --> 00:40:14,539
[SPEAKER_01] nego, ono, baš nekako su mi svi bili podrška.

483
00:40:14,539 --> 00:40:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] I danas mogu reći hvala im

484
00:40:16,079 --> 00:40:18,980
[SPEAKER_01] zato što mojih deset prijateljica

485
00:40:18,980 --> 00:40:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] s kojima se družimo,

486
00:40:20,079 --> 00:40:22,280
[SPEAKER_01] ono, već od rođenja,

487
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,219
[SPEAKER_01] i dalje su tu,

488
00:40:23,219 --> 00:40:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] ono, a ja sam godinama bila

489
00:40:25,559 --> 00:40:26,639
[SPEAKER_01] u svemu tome,

490
00:40:26,639 --> 00:40:27,820
[SPEAKER_01] ali one su i dalje tu

491
00:40:27,820 --> 00:40:28,900
[SPEAKER_01] i bile su uz mene

492
00:40:28,900 --> 00:40:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] dok sam radila i gradila

493
00:40:31,079 --> 00:40:32,920
[SPEAKER_01] i sad kad je sve to stalo.

494
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] Prekrasno, baš lijepo.

495
00:40:37,099 --> 00:40:39,139
[SPEAKER_00] A poteškoće,

496
00:40:39,139 --> 00:40:41,800
[SPEAKER_00] ono, prepreke na koje ste ne ilazili,

497
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] je li dolazilo do nekih odnosa

498
00:40:46,860 --> 00:40:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] koji su pucali ili,

499
00:40:48,300 --> 00:40:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] je li dolazilo do ne razumijevanja,

500
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:51,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali bilo tih priča

501
00:40:51,099 --> 00:40:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] da te nije neko razumio

502
00:40:52,699 --> 00:40:54,659
[SPEAKER_00] zbog tog što ti radiš ili?

503
00:40:54,659 --> 00:40:56,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ma, je, je, ono,

504
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:58,820
[SPEAKER_01] to je ljudi, pogotovo u Mostaru,

505
00:40:58,820 --> 00:40:59,980
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam sad kako je,

506
00:40:59,980 --> 00:41:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] je li tako, svugdje,

507
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je mal grad

508
00:41:03,340 --> 00:41:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] i više ćete podržati ljudi

509
00:41:06,119 --> 00:41:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji te ne poznaju,

510
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:07,880
[SPEAKER_01] ne koji te poznaju,

511
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:09,340
[SPEAKER_01] reći ima ne to siguran rad

512
00:41:09,340 --> 00:41:11,260
[SPEAKER_01] i zbog ničeg ima na neku koristu

513
00:41:11,260 --> 00:41:11,940
[SPEAKER_01] od tog, ona,

514
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, ja sam slušala,

515
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:16,159
[SPEAKER_01] ono, a, Bog zna ko su njeni roditelji,

516
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:18,519
[SPEAKER_01] i ono, što bi sad nekom pravdalo,

517
00:41:18,519 --> 00:41:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] mene je tad to stvarno jako boljalo

518
00:41:20,380 --> 00:41:21,940
[SPEAKER_01] i ko nju podržava,

519
00:41:21,940 --> 00:41:22,920
[SPEAKER_01] ko stoji za nje,

520
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:24,559
[SPEAKER_01] niko, ljudi, znači,

521
00:41:24,559 --> 00:41:25,760
[SPEAKER_01] apsolutno,

522
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] nitko nije stajao iza mene

523
00:41:27,699 --> 00:41:29,900
[SPEAKER_01] i da sam ja bila nečija figura

524
00:41:29,900 --> 00:41:31,340
[SPEAKER_01] da nešto budem slim,

525
00:41:31,340 --> 00:41:33,440
[SPEAKER_01] otkrilo bi se to nakon toliko godina

526
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] i to me možda najviše boljalo,

527
00:41:35,380 --> 00:41:37,320
[SPEAKER_01] jer svi su mislili da iza tog postoji

528
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:39,840
[SPEAKER_01] neki razlog za što ja sve to radim,

529
00:41:39,840 --> 00:41:42,599
[SPEAKER_01] a takvog razloga koji oni očekuju

530
00:41:42,599 --> 00:41:43,659
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno nije bilo.

531
00:41:44,059 --> 00:41:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] tada, taj period,

532
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] bila si zaručena,

533
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:48,239
[SPEAKER_00] je li to onda bio,

534
00:41:48,239 --> 00:41:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] tu je bila,

535
00:41:49,519 --> 00:41:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] je li možda to bila prijelomna odluka

536
00:41:51,199 --> 00:41:53,039
[SPEAKER_00] da zatvoriš akcije

537
00:41:53,039 --> 00:41:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] i da se posvetiš svom budućenjem suprugu,

538
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] braku i tom svemu,

539
00:41:56,559 --> 00:41:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] ili si nekako baš osjetila u srcu,

540
00:41:59,179 --> 00:42:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] ok, sad je ovo kraj

541
00:42:00,619 --> 00:42:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] i ono, neku božu intervenciju?

542
00:42:05,199 --> 00:42:10,280
[SPEAKER_01] Shvatila sam da način na koji ide ne može više ići,

543
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:13,260
[SPEAKER_01] da jako bi ikad opet,

544
00:42:13,260 --> 00:42:15,460
[SPEAKER_01] a meni je to baš velika želja,

545
00:42:15,460 --> 00:42:17,719
[SPEAKER_01] a vidi će moći li biti božja volja,

546
00:42:17,719 --> 00:42:20,920
[SPEAKER_01] i ako bi se nekad nešto pokrenulo tako,

547
00:42:20,920 --> 00:42:22,539
[SPEAKER_01] da bi skroz drugačije bilo,

548
00:42:22,539 --> 00:42:25,739
[SPEAKER_01] znači baš organizacija sa zaposlenim,

549
00:42:25,739 --> 00:42:26,239
[SPEAKER_01] sa svima,

550
00:42:26,239 --> 00:42:28,280
[SPEAKER_01] ako se to može omogući da bude tako ok,

551
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:31,019
[SPEAKER_01] ako ne da sve nosim to na leđima,

552
00:42:31,019 --> 00:42:33,480
[SPEAKER_01] baš nema smisla,

553
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da mi smo nesretni i umorni,

554
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] a da radimo tako neku stvar,

555
00:42:39,400 --> 00:42:40,440
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da ono,

556
00:42:40,440 --> 00:42:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] gubi se sva ljepota nekako tog,

557
00:42:44,039 --> 00:42:45,980
[SPEAKER_01] i darivanja i svega kad si ti nesretan,

558
00:42:45,980 --> 00:42:47,699
[SPEAKER_01] mislim kao ćeš biti nesretan

559
00:42:47,699 --> 00:42:49,139
[SPEAKER_01] ako želiš nešto dobro raditi,

560
00:42:49,139 --> 00:42:51,159
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da sve dobro potiče,

561
00:42:51,159 --> 00:42:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] je samo sreću i veselje i radost,

562
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] je to teško,

563
00:42:54,739 --> 00:42:55,800
[SPEAKER_01] a ne kažem to je super,

564
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:57,940
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam nasmijana i sve to,

565
00:42:58,280 --> 00:42:59,860
[SPEAKER_01] jako je to teško,

566
00:42:59,860 --> 00:43:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] ali kad se završi,

567
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] ako ti ovdje osjetiš da je to to.

568
00:43:04,039 --> 00:43:06,860
[SPEAKER_00] Da, baš to,

569
00:43:06,860 --> 00:43:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] nekad trebamo vidjeti sami sa sobom

570
00:43:10,199 --> 00:43:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] i onaj osjećaj,

571
00:43:11,440 --> 00:43:13,719
[SPEAKER_00] ali i odgovornost,

572
00:43:13,719 --> 00:43:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] realnost života,

573
00:43:14,800 --> 00:43:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] koju nam,

574
00:43:15,940 --> 00:43:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] koju smo dužni,

575
00:43:17,559 --> 00:43:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] i Bogu položi danas,

576
00:43:19,639 --> 00:43:20,940
[SPEAKER_00] kako smo odgovorni prema

577
00:43:20,940 --> 00:43:21,519
[SPEAKER_00] takvim stvarima.

578
00:43:21,519 --> 00:43:23,699
[SPEAKER_01] A jedna, oprosti, jedna od razloga je bilo

579
00:43:23,699 --> 00:43:24,679
[SPEAKER_01] zato što,

580
00:43:24,679 --> 00:43:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] trebao mi nekako i ozbiljan posao

581
00:43:27,659 --> 00:43:28,659
[SPEAKER_01] da nađem koju čovat,

582
00:43:28,659 --> 00:43:29,679
[SPEAKER_01] u čega ću živjeti.

583
00:43:29,679 --> 00:43:31,260
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, svima nama je potreba novac,

584
00:43:31,260 --> 00:43:31,699
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

585
00:43:31,699 --> 00:43:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] ne možeš ti živjeti,

586
00:43:33,699 --> 00:43:34,300
[SPEAKER_01] eto tako,

587
00:43:34,300 --> 00:43:35,360
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću rad dobre stvari,

588
00:43:35,360 --> 00:43:35,980
[SPEAKER_01] sve je super,

589
00:43:35,980 --> 00:43:37,199
[SPEAKER_01] mora to biti ozbiljnije,

590
00:43:37,199 --> 00:43:39,179
[SPEAKER_01] moram imat neku plaću za svoj rad,

591
00:43:39,179 --> 00:43:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

592
00:43:40,019 --> 00:43:42,179
[SPEAKER_01] da bi mogla i preživjeti,

593
00:43:42,179 --> 00:43:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] da bi mogla danas,

594
00:43:43,260 --> 00:43:43,559
[SPEAKER_01] sutra,

595
00:43:43,559 --> 00:43:43,980
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

596
00:43:43,980 --> 00:43:44,780
[SPEAKER_01] digant kredit,

597
00:43:46,380 --> 00:43:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] sebi napraviti dom,

598
00:43:47,980 --> 00:43:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] bilo šta,

599
00:43:48,619 --> 00:43:50,719
[SPEAKER_01] da bi mogla imati osnovne uvjete

600
00:43:50,719 --> 00:43:51,840
[SPEAKER_01] za život sebe,

601
00:43:51,840 --> 00:43:52,480
[SPEAKER_01] danas,

602
00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:53,639
[SPEAKER_01] sutra svoje djece,

603
00:43:53,639 --> 00:43:54,760
[SPEAKER_01] svoje obitelji,

604
00:43:54,760 --> 00:43:55,239
[SPEAKER_01] nekako,

605
00:43:55,239 --> 00:43:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] sve to vuklo da ono više nema nekog smisla.

606
00:43:58,340 --> 00:43:59,219
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da,

607
00:43:59,219 --> 00:44:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] a kako se ta tvoja slika tebe

608
00:44:02,079 --> 00:44:04,780
[SPEAKER_00] mijenjala kroz sve te godine rada

609
00:44:04,780 --> 00:44:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] od one jelene koja nosi,

610
00:44:07,400 --> 00:44:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] jedan paketič do ove jelene koja je

611
00:44:09,579 --> 00:44:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] zatvorila te akcije?

612
00:44:12,300 --> 00:44:14,099
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je sve to bilo nešto,

613
00:44:14,099 --> 00:44:14,300
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

614
00:44:14,300 --> 00:44:15,099
[SPEAKER_01] spontano,

615
00:44:15,099 --> 00:44:17,360
[SPEAKER_01] tako da nisam doživljavila ni velike,

616
00:44:17,360 --> 00:44:19,760
[SPEAKER_01] ni male akcije ko nešto,

617
00:44:19,760 --> 00:44:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] wow,

618
00:44:20,059 --> 00:44:20,599
[SPEAKER_01] nekako,

619
00:44:20,599 --> 00:44:20,840
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

620
00:44:20,840 --> 00:44:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] svakodnevno se mi je postalo,

621
00:44:22,380 --> 00:44:23,679
[SPEAKER_01] možda to je nije dobro,

622
00:44:23,679 --> 00:44:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

623
00:44:23,900 --> 00:44:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] čovjek,

624
00:44:24,380 --> 00:44:25,780
[SPEAKER_01] sve mu postane nekako,

625
00:44:25,780 --> 00:44:26,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne sve jedno,

626
00:44:26,619 --> 00:44:26,940
[SPEAKER_01] nego,

627
00:44:26,940 --> 00:44:29,019
[SPEAKER_01] veljda ono,

628
00:44:29,019 --> 00:44:32,199
[SPEAKER_01] nauči živjeti da se stalno to nešto događa.

629
00:44:32,199 --> 00:44:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] Meni sad,

630
00:44:32,760 --> 00:44:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] ja osvrano,

631
00:44:33,800 --> 00:44:34,059
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

632
00:44:34,059 --> 00:44:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] imala sam dana kad se rekla,

633
00:44:35,739 --> 00:44:35,860
[SPEAKER_01] e,

634
00:44:35,860 --> 00:44:36,440
[SPEAKER_01] tri dana,

635
00:44:36,440 --> 00:44:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] gasim obitel,

636
00:44:37,420 --> 00:44:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] želim se odmorto,

637
00:44:38,579 --> 00:44:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] sve ga ja temperaturu dobijem,

638
00:44:39,880 --> 00:44:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] valjda mi je tijelo naviklo bilo da,

639
00:44:41,880 --> 00:44:42,159
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

640
00:44:42,159 --> 00:44:46,900
[SPEAKER_01] da imam neki mir i navikla sam tako da sam uvijek u nekoj žurbi,

641
00:44:46,900 --> 00:44:48,480
[SPEAKER_01] tako da,

642
00:44:48,480 --> 00:44:50,960
[SPEAKER_01] sve je to nekako prolazilo.

643
00:44:50,960 --> 00:44:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] Žao mi je samo što,

644
00:44:52,619 --> 00:44:56,179
[SPEAKER_01] strah me da ću izgubiti empatiju,

645
00:44:56,179 --> 00:45:00,159
[SPEAKER_01] jer svaki dan sam bila okružena godinama s ljudima koji su,

646
00:45:00,159 --> 00:45:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

647
00:45:00,699 --> 00:45:02,739
[SPEAKER_01] sa teškim životnim pričama,

648
00:45:02,739 --> 00:45:03,019
[SPEAKER_01] onda,

649
00:45:03,019 --> 00:45:05,079
[SPEAKER_01] u jednom trenutku vidjela sam da,

650
00:45:05,079 --> 00:45:05,239
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

651
00:45:05,239 --> 00:45:07,159
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi pričaju svane teške životne priče,

652
00:45:07,159 --> 00:45:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] da i ja slušam,

653
00:45:08,099 --> 00:45:08,400
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

654
00:45:08,579 --> 00:45:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] dobro,

655
00:45:08,960 --> 00:45:09,219
[SPEAKER_01] ja,

656
00:45:09,219 --> 00:45:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] kao ćemo sad to riješiti,

657
00:45:10,860 --> 00:45:11,579
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

658
00:45:11,579 --> 00:45:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] da sam izgubila nekako srce u svom tom,

659
00:45:15,579 --> 00:45:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

660
00:45:15,800 --> 00:45:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] da osjetim tu neku puninu u srcu,

661
00:45:18,019 --> 00:45:20,280
[SPEAKER_01] da na pravi način pomažem,

662
00:45:20,280 --> 00:45:20,460
[SPEAKER_01] nego,

663
00:45:20,460 --> 00:45:20,760
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

664
00:45:20,760 --> 00:45:23,159
[SPEAKER_01] bila sam se zasjetila nekako svega,

665
00:45:23,159 --> 00:45:23,940
[SPEAKER_01] tog i to mi je,

666
00:45:23,940 --> 00:45:25,980
[SPEAKER_01] možda je dobro,

667
00:45:25,980 --> 00:45:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

668
00:45:26,460 --> 00:45:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] ja uvijek kažem,

669
00:45:27,519 --> 00:45:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] najteže stvari u životu kad smo se događali,

670
00:45:29,880 --> 00:45:30,739
[SPEAKER_01] i kad sam ono rekla,

671
00:45:30,739 --> 00:45:31,139
[SPEAKER_01] Bože,

672
00:45:31,139 --> 00:45:32,960
[SPEAKER_01] zašto meni opet,

673
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:33,940
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

674
00:45:33,940 --> 00:45:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam sam rekla,

675
00:45:34,960 --> 00:45:35,260
[SPEAKER_01] Bože,

676
00:45:35,260 --> 00:45:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] hvala što je s to dogodilo,

677
00:45:36,519 --> 00:45:38,900
[SPEAKER_01] je poslije tog došlo nešto bolje,

678
00:45:38,900 --> 00:45:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

679
00:45:39,260 --> 00:45:39,679
[SPEAKER_01] da,

680
00:45:39,679 --> 00:45:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] gledala sam ono,

681
00:45:41,400 --> 00:45:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] u intervju jednom si rekla,

682
00:45:43,500 --> 00:45:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] da si počela gubit sebe,

683
00:45:45,300 --> 00:45:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] u tim akcijama,

684
00:45:46,480 --> 00:45:48,059
[SPEAKER_00] na što si točno mislila,

685
00:45:48,059 --> 00:45:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] kako gubit sebe,

686
00:45:49,199 --> 00:45:50,099
[SPEAKER_00] je li to bilo ono,

687
00:45:50,099 --> 00:45:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] premalo postavljanja granica,

688
00:45:51,940 --> 00:45:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] u odnosima s drugima,

689
00:45:53,639 --> 00:45:56,280
[SPEAKER_00] ili previše tereta za tebe?

690
00:45:56,280 --> 00:45:56,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ma,

691
00:45:56,659 --> 00:45:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] preraslo je mene,

692
00:45:58,019 --> 00:45:58,840
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno,

693
00:45:58,840 --> 00:45:59,159
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

694
00:45:59,159 --> 00:46:00,760
[SPEAKER_01] jedna osoba,

695
00:46:00,760 --> 00:46:01,460
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

696
00:46:01,460 --> 00:46:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] stotine volontera,

697
00:46:03,000 --> 00:46:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] i volontera,

698
00:46:04,039 --> 00:46:05,559
[SPEAKER_01] moraš iskoordinirati,

699
00:46:06,179 --> 00:46:10,019
[SPEAKER_01] svega je bilo previše nekako,

700
00:46:10,019 --> 00:46:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] tad to nisam shvaćala,

701
00:46:11,440 --> 00:46:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali,

702
00:46:11,699 --> 00:46:13,719
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam se baš bila umorla,

703
00:46:13,719 --> 00:46:14,119
[SPEAKER_01] i,

704
00:46:14,119 --> 00:46:14,880
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da,

705
00:46:14,880 --> 00:46:15,199
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

706
00:46:15,199 --> 00:46:16,820
[SPEAKER_01] koliko god je danas ljudima žao,

707
00:46:16,820 --> 00:46:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo sad,

708
00:46:17,559 --> 00:46:19,599
[SPEAKER_01] period koji sam ostala bez posla,

709
00:46:19,599 --> 00:46:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] svi ono govori,

710
00:46:20,239 --> 00:46:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] jel ti to znak,

711
00:46:21,199 --> 00:46:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] vrati se,

712
00:46:21,960 --> 00:46:22,559
[SPEAKER_01] ja ono,

713
00:46:22,559 --> 00:46:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] neću,

714
00:46:23,380 --> 00:46:24,760
[SPEAKER_01] onaj,

715
00:46:24,760 --> 00:46:27,139
[SPEAKER_01] žao i meni,

716
00:46:27,139 --> 00:46:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

717
00:46:27,340 --> 00:46:31,599
[SPEAKER_01] meni je baš bilo teško i lijepo to sve zatvoriti,

718
00:46:31,599 --> 00:46:33,460
[SPEAKER_01] jer nije zatvoreno,

719
00:46:33,780 --> 00:46:37,519
[SPEAKER_01] ta zemca je zatvorna na vrhuncu svog djelovanja,

720
00:46:37,519 --> 00:46:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] kad bolje i više i nije moglo vići,

721
00:46:40,199 --> 00:46:42,380
[SPEAKER_01] sve akcije su prolazile super,

722
00:46:42,380 --> 00:46:44,300
[SPEAKER_01] bile su velike praćene,

723
00:46:44,300 --> 00:46:45,460
[SPEAKER_01] sve je to bilo super,

724
00:46:45,460 --> 00:46:48,719
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja sam jednostavno osjetla da je vrijeme da stanemo.

725
00:46:48,719 --> 00:46:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] Tu u kraj.

726
00:46:50,320 --> 00:46:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ušla si poslije toga u brak i što je za tebe značila neka ljubav i služenje u braku,

727
00:46:56,440 --> 00:47:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] naučila si kako to s drugim, onda to tebe lako ide sad.

728
00:47:00,059 --> 00:47:05,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ma nije, nije užasno zato što ima muškaricu u kući i šta će mi on u kući,

729
00:47:05,219 --> 00:47:06,400
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam odrasla s vama.

730
00:47:06,400 --> 00:47:13,059
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da mi je to bilo čudno što sad on radi tu i teško nekako bila mi.

731
00:47:13,059 --> 00:47:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svijekim se svima je to bilo smiješno,

732
00:47:15,000 --> 00:47:15,699
[SPEAKER_01] ako to je govorim,

733
00:47:15,699 --> 00:47:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] pa nemam pojma kako ćemo mi živiti skupa,

734
00:47:18,019 --> 00:47:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] ti si muškaric u kući.

735
00:47:21,079 --> 00:47:24,539
[SPEAKER_01] Zanimala sam brat, odbrat je bio djete, nije bilo to, to nekako,

736
00:47:24,539 --> 00:47:28,800
[SPEAKER_01] ali baš je nekako, ne zna što ljudi kažu,

737
00:47:28,800 --> 00:47:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] no ovaj se u životu promijeni kad tu pišu brak,

738
00:47:31,039 --> 00:47:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] meni je sve isto se nastavilo čak i bolje

739
00:47:34,019 --> 00:47:36,219
[SPEAKER_01] i previše nas plaše s tim brakom.

740
00:47:36,219 --> 00:47:38,940
[SPEAKER_01] Svi su mi govorili, vidit ćeš ti kad se udaš,

741
00:47:38,940 --> 00:47:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] sam govorio, vidit ćeš ti kad dođu djeca.

742
00:47:40,980 --> 00:47:44,980
[SPEAKER_01] Mi jednostavno čekamo da nešto vidimo kako je to grozno,

743
00:47:44,980 --> 00:47:46,480
[SPEAKER_01] a mislim da je sve to super.

744
00:47:46,480 --> 00:47:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, naravno da je teško,

745
00:47:47,980 --> 00:47:51,219
[SPEAKER_01] kad imaš malo djete, naravno da ima teškoće,

746
00:47:51,219 --> 00:47:52,559
[SPEAKER_01] ali da je prelijepo nešto

747
00:47:52,559 --> 00:47:55,500
[SPEAKER_01] i da ne trebamo mlade uopće plašiti s tim.

748
00:47:55,500 --> 00:48:04,219
[SPEAKER_00] Kad bi mogla Jelena od 19 godina nešto reći,

749
00:48:04,219 --> 00:48:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] poručiti o što bih rekla?

750
00:48:05,760 --> 00:48:10,559
[SPEAKER_01] Da se ne boji, da zrivi, da...

751
00:48:10,559 --> 00:48:12,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bila baš iz prepadana.

752
00:48:12,739 --> 00:48:16,219
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek se ljudi nasmiju kad to kažem,

753
00:48:16,300 --> 00:48:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] ali bojala sam se dati ono intervju i nešto pričati,

754
00:48:20,119 --> 00:48:22,260
[SPEAKER_01] jer šta će ljudi reći ako ja nešto krivo?

755
00:48:22,260 --> 00:48:24,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem jer ja znam koliko puno pričam,

756
00:48:24,519 --> 00:48:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek neku glupost.

757
00:48:25,539 --> 00:48:27,059
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ono šta ako se to dogodi,

758
00:48:27,059 --> 00:48:28,579
[SPEAKER_01] ako neko nešto loše kaže.

759
00:48:28,579 --> 00:48:30,820
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ja izađem neki članok,

760
00:48:30,820 --> 00:48:33,679
[SPEAKER_01] ja ovako sjedim i čekam da se dogodi

761
00:48:33,679 --> 00:48:34,940
[SPEAKER_01] taj neki ružan komentar.

762
00:48:34,940 --> 00:48:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] Sve prelijepi komentar koji mene ne zanimaju,

763
00:48:37,460 --> 00:48:40,519
[SPEAKER_01] ja ih ono samo stajem i dogodi se neki gdje kažu,

764
00:48:40,519 --> 00:48:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] ma ja stoji zanje ovaj, stoji zanje ovaj,

765
00:48:43,539 --> 00:48:46,280
[SPEAKER_01] ona vaka, ona naka jasna skira.

766
00:48:46,280 --> 00:48:47,139
[SPEAKER_01] I meni to ono gori,

767
00:48:47,139 --> 00:48:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] ali ti sjediš čekaš da dođe neki ružani?

768
00:48:49,960 --> 00:48:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] Oko te ne komentira znači da smo zanimljiva,

769
00:48:52,059 --> 00:48:54,119
[SPEAKER_01] da te ne komentira nikako ono,

770
00:48:54,119 --> 00:48:56,440
[SPEAKER_01] bilo bi bezveze to što radiš,

771
00:48:56,440 --> 00:48:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] već da radiš, neš da velja,

772
00:48:57,559 --> 00:48:58,380
[SPEAKER_01] nemoj se sakirati.

773
00:48:58,380 --> 00:49:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne, ja sam uvijek sjedila i čekala

774
00:49:00,679 --> 00:49:01,900
[SPEAKER_01] šta ti se loše dogodi.

775
00:49:01,900 --> 00:49:04,099
[SPEAKER_01] I danas dan sam takva i to pokušala.

776
00:49:04,099 --> 00:49:05,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ja gori im izdajem slikovicu,

777
00:49:05,840 --> 00:49:07,719
[SPEAKER_01] sve ide super, ja čekam,

778
00:49:07,719 --> 00:49:08,719
[SPEAKER_01] moram se nešto loše dogodi,

779
00:49:08,719 --> 00:49:10,119
[SPEAKER_01] ne može sve ovako dobro iće.

780
00:49:10,119 --> 00:49:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to nekako i danas dan.

781
00:49:13,000 --> 00:49:14,599
[SPEAKER_01] I s 19 godina i danas dan

782
00:49:14,599 --> 00:49:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] trebam otkloniti od sebe da živim,

783
00:49:18,039 --> 00:49:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] da budu i dobri loši trenuci.

784
00:49:20,079 --> 00:49:21,400
[SPEAKER_01] Život je sastavljeno od toga.

785
00:49:21,400 --> 00:49:23,260
[SPEAKER_01] Da ne moram, navikla sam,

786
00:49:23,260 --> 00:49:24,920
[SPEAKER_01] mislim i kroz djetinstvo i kroz život

787
00:49:24,920 --> 00:49:26,539
